00:00:02.880 --> 00:00:11.220
- RICE WITH TOMATO AND TURKEY MEAT -
 
This time I bring you a white rice with turkey meat and a fried egg. I hope you like it.

00:00:11.800 --> 00:00:32.480
--- INGREDIENTS 4 people ---
 
350gr of meat Minced Turkey
200gr of Rice
1 chopped onion
2 cloves of garlic
50gr of Piquillo Peppers
Ketchup
4 Eggs
Salt
Olive oil

00:00:36.680 --> 00:00:41.620
1. Chop 1 clove of garlic and sauté it in a casserole with a little olive oil.

00:00:41.900 --> 00:00:46.680
2. Add the tomato sauce to the garlic sautéed.

00:00:47.180 --> 00:00:50.680
3. Let cook over low heat, for a few minutes.

00:00:54.880 --> 00:01:01.560
4. In another pan add the other clove of garlic cut into slices and sauté it too.

00:01:02.700 --> 00:01:09.880
5. Add the rice and sauté it with the garlic.

00:01:10.720 --> 00:01:18.380
6. Cover with water and season with salt. Let cook about 10 minutes. Then we drained it and reserved it.

00:01:22.960 --> 00:01:25.760
7. Take a pan and add a little olive oil.

00:01:26.100 --> 00:01:32.860
8. Add the finely chopped onion and sauté well.

00:01:38.240 --> 00:01:45.220
9. When we have the onion sautéed, add the turkey meat, brown it and season it with salt.

00:01:52.960 --> 00:02:00.540
10. Once we have the turkey meat sautéed, add the tomato sauce and let cook everything together for about 10 minutes.

00:02:07.680 --> 00:02:15.280
11. Chop the piquillo peppers and add it to the meat and we will have it ready.

00:02:25.780 --> 00:02:32.220
12. Fry the eggs

00:02:50.880 --> 00:02:57.220
We mount the plate with the rice, the meat and the fried egg and ready to eat.

